tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE climate_data (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    location TEXT,
    temperature DECIMAL,
    humidity DECIMAL,
    rainfall DECIMAL
);

CREATE TABLE agroforestry_practices (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    crop_name TEXT,
    planting_date DATE,
    harvest_date DATE,
    area DECIMAL,
    soil_type TEXT
);

CREATE TABLE analysis_results (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    analysis_date DATE,
    analysis_type TEXT,
    result TEXT,
    conclusions TEXT
);

CREATE TABLE location (
    location_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    city VARCHAR(50),
    country VARCHAR(50),
    latitude FLOAT,
    longitude FLOAT
);

CREATE TABLE analysis_results (
    result_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    date DATE,
    conclusion TEXT,
    practice_id INT,
    location_id INT,
    FOREIGN KEY (practice_id) REFERENCES agroforestry_practices(practice_id),
    FOREIGN KEY (location_id) REFERENCES location(location_id)
);
